"2 pounds unpeeled red potatoes, cubed","1/4  red onion, finely chopped","2  celery stalks, finely chopped","1  dill pickle, finely chopped","1/2 cup mayonnaise","1/2 cup sour cream","1 tablespoon apple cider vinegar","3 tablespoons minced fresh basil","3 tablespoons minced fresh chives","3 tablespoons minced fresh flat-leaf parsley","3  hard-cooked eggs, chopped","1 teaspoon kosher salt","1/2 teaspoon cracked black pepper","  Garnishes: chopped fresh basil, chives, and flat-leaf parsley"